N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 23.6 - List of approved vehicles

State Regulations

The Department of Motor Vehicles shall compile and maintain
a list of motor vehicles approved for historical registration based upon unique
characteristics. Notes
